title: Exploding Buck
author: Falkenzz
pages:
#- Obtain Potassium
Press in buckshot mold and freeze
Coat potassium buckshot. Permatex Spray-A-Gasket Hi-Temp sealant is a good option. The spray should coat the entire surface, as the potassium needs to be fully sealed. 
Load shells

#- Test the ammo on something with a high water content
If the shot has no deformation, apply a thinner coat and retest.

NOTICE: EDUCATIONAL PURPOSES ONLY
#- 